Estrutura de diretórios:
bind-dns-blocklist/
├── zones/
│   └── db.blocked
└── named.conf.local

zones/db.blocked
Zona para bloquear sites (genérico)
$TTL 86400
@       IN SOA   ns.block.local. root.ns.block.local. (
        2025092201 ; Serial
        604800     ; Refresh
        86400      ; Retry
        2419200    ; Expire
        86400 )    ; Negative Cache TTL
;
@       IN      NS      localhost.
@       IN      A       127.0.0.1
*       IN      A       127.0.0.1   ; Redireciona todos os subdomínios para localhost

named.conf.local:
zone "pornhub.com" {
    type master;
    file "/etc/bind/zones/db.blocked";
};

